tips.name: Disney's live-action Beauty and the Beast
tips.part1: Having spent most of her life exploring the jungle, nothing could prepare Dora for her most dangerous adventure yet -- high school. Accompanied by a ragtag group of teens and Boots the monkey, Dora embarks on a quest to save her parents while trying to solve the seemingly impossible mystery behind a lost Incan civilization.

guide.name: Devotion (2022)
guide.part1:
The harrowing true story of two elite US Navy fighter pilots during the Korean War. Their heroic sacrifices would ultimately make them the Navy's most celebrated wingmen. 
            
            War, History, Drama

            
            J.D. Dillard : Director
            Jonathan Stewart : Screenplay 
            Jake Crane : Screenplay

guide.name: Black Adam (2022)
guide.part1:
Nearly 5,000 years after he was bestowed with the almighty powers of the Egyptian gods—and imprisoned just as quickly—Black Adam is freed from his earthly tomb, ready to unleash his unique form of justice on the modern world.
            
            (US) Action, Fantasy, Science Fiction.  2h 5m

            
            
            C.C. Beck : Characters
            Bill Parker : Characters
            Jaume Collet-Serra : Director
            Rory Haines : Writer
            Sohrab Noshirvani : Writer
            Adam Sztykiel : Writer

guide.name: Black Panther: Wakanda Forever (2022)
guide.part1:
Queen Ramonda, Shuri, M’Baku, Okoye and the Dora Milaje fight to protect their nation from intervening world powers in the wake of King T’Challa’s death. As the Wakandans strive to embrace their next chapter, the heroes must band together with the help of War Dog Nakia and Everett Ross and forge a new path for the kingdom of Wakanda.
            

            
            Ryan Coogler : Director, Screenplay, Story
            Stan Lee : Characters
            Jack Kirby. : Characters
            Joe Robert Cole : Screenplay

guide.name: R.I.P.D. 2: Rise of the Damned (2022)
guide.part1:
When Sheriff Roy Pulsipher finds himself in the afterlife, he joins a special police force and returns to Earth to save humanity from the undead 
            
            
            Fantasy, Action, Comedy, Crime 1h 42m.
            
            Paul Leyden : Director, Writer  
            Andrew Klein : Writer

guide.name: Paradise City (2022)
guide.part1:
Renegade bounty hunter Ryan Swan must carve his way through the Hawaiian crime world to wreak vengeance on the kingpin who murdered his father.
            
            Crime, Action, Thriller. 1h 33m
            
            
            Chuck Russell :  Director
            Edward Drake : Writer  
            Corey Large : Writer

guide.name: Hex (2022)
guide.part1:
Following a mysterious disappearance on a jump, a group of skydivers experience paranormal occurrences that leave them fighting for their lives.
            
            
            
            Action, Horror, Thriller. 1h 28m
            
            
            Andy Malchiodi : Director.
            Chris Johnston :  Director
            Hans Rodionoff : Writer

guide.name: Disenchanted (2022)
guide.part1:
Disillusioned with life in the city, feeling out of place in suburbia, and frustrated that her happily ever after hasn’t been so easy to find, Giselle turns to the magic of Andalasia for help. Accidentally transforming the entire town into a real-life fairy tale and placing her family’s future happiness in jeopardy, she must race against time to reverse the spell and determine what happily ever after truly means to her and her family.
            
            
            
            Comedy, Family, Fantasy 1h 59m
            
            
            Bill Kelly :  Characters 
            Adam Shankman :  Director 
            Brigitte Hales :  Screenplay
            Richard LaGravenese : Story 
            David N. Weiss : Story
            J. David Stem : Story

guide.name: Emily the Criminal (2022)
guide.part1:
Emily, who is saddled with student debt and locked out of the job market due to a minor criminal record, gets involved in a credit card scam that pulls her into the criminal underworld of Los Angeles, ultimately leading to deadly consequences
            
            Crime, Drama, Mystery, Thriller. 1h 37m.
            
            John Patton Ford : Director, Writer
